						<summary>

						<p>Pillar lying in front of the Viśvēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>KĀḶAYUKTI.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in cyclic year Kāḷayukti, Śrāvaṇa, śu. 4 Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Slightly damaged, Refers to the walk by Ārādhyula Ammarāju and Kumudavelli Lingaya to fix the boundries from the village Nūrālamkōṭa.</p>						

						</summary>
