<!--<h4>FIRST SIDE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṁlā 
<lb n="2"/>numa 
<lb n="3"/>cā maṁ 
<lb n="4"/>durājya 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṁduvrā 
<lb n="6"/>ya 
</p>

<!--<h4>SECOND SIDE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7"/>śrīkālayukti 
<lb n="8"/>saṁvatsara śrāvaṇa śu 
<lb n="9"/>14 Ā sūpūḍi vu 
<lb n="10"/>ttaramu kumudavelli 
<lb n="11"/>dakṣiṇamu tūrpu 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>lakunnu Ārā 
<lb n="13"/>dhyula Aṁmirājunaḍa 
<lb n="14"/>vagā kumudavelli liṁga 
<lb n="15"/>ya venaka naḍacenu nūrā 
<lb n="16"/>laṁ kōṭanuṁḍi kāme A 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṁma ceruvu dakṣiṇa māda 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ceruvu tūrpubaṁḍṭa 
<lb n="19"/>maḍilakaḍa kūḍi Ā 
</p>

<!--<h4>FOURTH FACE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="20" break="no"/><unclear>tu</unclear>kūri sōmana 
<lb n="21"/>ceruvu paḍamaṭī 
<lb n="22"/>Allu polimēra <unclear>kaḍa</unclear> 
<lb n="23"/>baṁdaṭi <unclear>gha</unclear>ṭṭa cēśi Ā 
<lb n="24" break="no"/>rādyula Aṁmmirāju 
<lb n="25"/>naḍicenu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yidi Ācaṁ 
<lb n="26" break="no"/>dasdhāyigā tagu 
<lb n="27"/>gaḍaṁ 
<lb n="28"/><unclear>yinū</unclear> 
</p>

<!--<h4>SECOND SECTION FIRST SIDE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="29"/>Attili sidana Ācā 
<lb n="30" break="no"/>rdigāri guttanu 
<lb n="31"/>polimēra nikhācēśi 
<lb n="32"/>peddalu kākita rā 
<lb n="33" break="no"/>ju kṛṣṇapānu [Ā] 
<lb n="34" break="no"/>mati tharmapuri gā 
<lb n="35" break="no"/>ḍi rāju tiṁmarā 
<lb n="36" break="no"/>juku nātarā 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="37" break="no"/>ju veṁkkaṭaya<unclear>ku</unclear> 
<lb n="38-42"/><ce>completely worn out</ce>
<lb n="43"/>deśari Ayyavirāju 
</p>

